title: Benghazi hearing shows GOP nominee will need to hold Hillary Clinton to account
text: Former Hewlett-Packard CEO and 2016 GOP presidential candidate Carly Fiorina said Friday that Thursday's hearing held by the Select Committee on Benghazi showed that the eventual Republican nominee is going to have to hold former Secretary of State Hillary Rodham Clinton to account.
